---
title: Amphibious Tours in Santa Barbara, CA
description: Experience Santa Barbara from land and sea on Land Shark Tours — the only amphibious vehicle tour on the California coast. See dolphins, whales, and harbor wildlife departing from Stearns Wharf.
keywords: Santa Barbara amphibious tours, Land Shark Tours, Santa Barbara whale watching, things to do in Santa Barbara, Santa Barbara harbor tours, land and sea tours California, Stearns Wharf tours
---

{% extends "layouts/base.njk" %}

{% block head %}
  <script src="https://reservationgenie.com/{{ client.rgPath }}/popup.js"></script>
{% endblock %}

{% block content %}

  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="relative bg-navy-900 text-white overflow-hidden min-h-[85vh] flex items-center">

    <!-- Decorative anchor watermark -->
    <div class="absolute right-0 bottom-0 top-0 hidden lg:flex items-center pr-16 text-[360px] opacity-5 leading-none select-none">⚓</div>

    <div class="relative z-10 max-w-screen-xl mx-auto px-4 lg:px-6 py-24">
      <div class="max-w-2xl">
        <span class="inline-block bg-teal text-white text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest px-4 py-2 rounded-full mb-6">Santa Barbara's Original Amphibious Tour</span>
        <h1 class="text-5xl lg:text-7xl font-heading leading-none mb-6">Land. Sea.<br>Adventure.</h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-navy-200 mb-10 max-w-xl leading-relaxed font-body">
          90 minutes of non-stop fun through Santa Barbara's streets and straight into the Pacific Ocean. Dolphins, sea lions, whales — and the most unique vehicle you'll ever ride.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4">
          <a href="https://book.{{ client.bookingDomain }}.com/{{ client.rgPath }}/reservations/calendar" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="btn-primary">
            Book Your Tour &rarr;
          </a>
          <a href="{{ "/public-tours/" | url }}" class="btn-outline-white">
            Learn More
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Wave into about section -->
    <svg class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 right-0 w-full" viewBox="0 0 1440 80" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" preserveAspectRatio="none">
      <path d="M0,40 C360,80 1080,0 1440,40 L1440,80 L0,80 Z" fill="white"/>
    </svg>

  </section>

  <!-- Highlights strip -->
  <section class="bg-teal text-white">
    <div class="max-w-screen-xl mx-auto px-4 lg:px-6 py-10">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-6 text-center">
        <div>
          <div class="text-4xl mb-2">🌊</div>
          <div class="font-heading text-xl">90-Minute Tour</div>
          <div class="text-teal-100 text-sm mt-1">Half land, half sea</div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="text-4xl mb-2">🐬</div>
          <div class="font-heading text-xl">Wildlife Encounters</div>
          <div class="text-teal-100 text-sm mt-1">Dolphins, seals &amp; whales</div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="text-4xl mb-2">🎉</div>
          <div class="font-heading text-xl">Fun for All Ages</div>
          <div class="text-teal-100 text-sm mt-1">Kids under 2 ride free</div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="text-4xl mb-2">🏆</div>
          <div class="font-heading text-xl">Award Winning</div>
          <div class="text-teal-100 text-sm mt-1">Top 10 in California</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- About -->
  <section id="about" class="bg-white py-16 lg:py-24">
    <div class="max-w-screen-xl mx-auto px-4 lg:px-6">
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
        <div>
          <h2 class="section-title">About Our Tours</h2>
          <p class="text-teal font-body font-semibold mb-6">Voted the best city and harbor tours of Santa Barbara and top 10 cool things to do in California.</p>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4 leading-relaxed">Climb aboard Santa Barbara's original amphibious tour vehicle, the LAND SHARK, for a personally narrated 90-minute land and sea tour adventure. Experience the best of Santa Barbara, in comfort aboard the most modern state-of-the-art amphibious vehicle in the world!</p>
          <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">Enjoy exquisite views of the Santa Barbara coastline, the American Riviera, and the Santa Ynez mountains as seen only from our boat at sea. Don't miss this exciting and entertaining Land and Sea adventure to experience Santa Barbara as never before! Fun for all ages, a ride aboard the Land Shark is truly a Santa Barbara and California "must-do" attraction.</p>
          <div class="mt-8 flex flex-wrap gap-4">
            <a href="{{ "/public-tours/" | url }}" class="btn-navy">See Tour Info</a>
            <a href="{{ "/charter/" | url }}" class="btn-teal">Private Charters</a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="aspect-video rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-xl">
          <iframe class="w-full h-full" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/Cpw-702p7Q0" title="Land Shark Tours Santa Barbara" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Contact form -->
  <section id="contact" class="bg-sand">
    <div class="max-w-screen-xl mx-auto px-4 lg:px-6 pt-12">
